24
00:01:53,831 --> 00:01:56,008
<font color=#FFFF5E><i>The world came together as one.</i></font>

25
00:01:56,363 --> 00:01:58,549
<font color=#FFFF5E><i>And we fought back.</i></font>

26
00:01:59,305 --> 00:02:01,985
<font color=#FFFF5E><i>Scientists from 17 countries...</i></font>

27
00:02:02,383 --> 00:02:03,743
<font color=#FFFF5E><i>led by the U.S. and China...</i></font>

28
00:02:04,506 --> 00:02:05,748
<font color=#FFFF5E><i>worked tirelessly...</i></font>

29
00:02:07,188 --> 00:02:09,434
