34
00:02:20,978 --> 00:02:23,563
<font color=#FFFF5E><i>designed to impact the
basic elements of weather...</i></font>

35
00:02:23,764 --> 00:02:26,359
<font color=#FFFF5E><i>heat, pressure, and water.</i></font>

36
00:02:26,954 --> 00:02:30,183
<font color=#FFFF5E><i>All overseen by the
