71
00:04:33,200 --> 00:04:35,815
<font color=#FFFF5E>It's just the you said, "we" built it?</font>

72
00:04:36,016 --> 00:04:37,672
<font color=#FFFF5E>Yes, indeed I did.</font>

73
00:04:38,373 --> 00:04:39,750
<font color=#FFFF5E>Because I know what I did.</font>

74
00:04:39,854 --> 00:04:42,147
<font color=#FFFF5E>I'm the guy that led the team
