<font color=#FFFF5E>You leave me no choice.
I told you.</font>

150
00:08:11,426 --> 00:08:12,786
<font color=#FFFF5E>This had to go well,
and it didn't.</font>

151
00:08:14,721 --> 00:08:17,976
<font color=#FFFF5E>Look, I-I'm sorry, Jake.</font>

152
00:08:21,373 --> 00:08:22,695
<font color=#FFFF5E>You're fired.</font>

153
00:08:46,469 --> 00:08:49,308
<font color=#FFFF5E>Jesus. It's over 120
in this mother.</font>

154
00:09:28,590 --> 00:09:29,590
<font color=#FFFF5E>Fan out.</font>

155
00:10:05,288 --> 00:10:06,610
<font color=#FFFF5E>Uh, Agent Wilson.</font>

156
