163
00:10:27,130 --> 00:10:28,363
<font color=#FFFF5E>Sarah, come on,
can we just drop...</font>

164
00:10:28,364 --> 00:10:29,444
<font color=#FFFF5E>Assistant Secretary Lawson.</font>

165
00:10:30,041 --> 00:10:32,046
<font color=#FFFF5E>I'm not permitted to engage in</font>

166
