<font color=#FFFF5E>You're interfering with my duties.
I'd rather not shoot you.</font>

172
00:10:45,849 --> 00:10:47,166
<font color=#FFFF5E>Well, it would be an honor</font>

173
00:10:47,270 --> 00:10:49,020
<font color=#FFFF5E>to be the first person
