<font color=#FFFF5E>I didn't say anything.</font>

182
00:11:09,889 --> 00:11:11,390
<font color=#FFFF5E>Move along, sir.</font>

183
00:11:11,692 --> 00:11:12,792
<font color=#FFFF5E>Yes, ma'am.</font>

184
