- It's the perfect weapon, sir.</font>

1339
01:18:02,118 --> 01:18:04,438
<font color=#FFFF5E>All right? Dekkom is trying
to change the map of the world.</font>

1340
01:18:04,552 --> 01:18:06,152
<font color=#FFFF5E>Then what? Blame it on
a computer glitch?</font>

1341
01:18:06,261 --> 01:18:08,868
<font color=#FFFF5E>Yeah, that and a dead president.</font>

1342
01:18:08,969 --> 01:18:10,885
<font color=#FFFF5E>He'll take office
after wiping out</font>

1343
01:18:10,910 --> 01:18:12,907
<font color=#FFFF5E>everyone in the
line of succession.</font>

1344
01:18:23,259 --> 01:18:24,306
<font color=#FFFF5E>Dear God.</font>

1345
01:18:45,018 --> 01:18:46,882
<font color=#FFFF5E>- Get to cover, under the bridge!
- Sir.</font>

1346
01:19:29,007 --> 01:19:31,399
<font color=#FFFF5E>You are implicating the
Secretary of State in this.</font>

1347
01:19:31,499 --> 01:19:32,629
<font color=#FFFF5E>You realize you're committing...</font>

1348
01:19:32,630 --> 01:19:33,464
<font color=#FFFF5E>- treason?
- Treason.</font>

1349
01:19:33,490 --> 01:19:36,133
<font color=#FFFF5E>Oh, yeah, I kidnapped the President,
I've stolen state secrets.</font>

1350
01:19:36,190 --> 01:19:38,436
<font color=#FFFF5E>Anything I'm forgetting, honey?</font>

1351
01:19:38,993 --> 01:19:40,208
<font color=#FFFF5E>Honey?</font>

1352
01:19:40,610 --> 01:19:41,610
<font color=#FFFF5E>Guilty.</font>

1353
01:19:41,742 --> 01:19:43,462
<font color=#FFFF5E>It took years for
Dekkom to plan this, sir.</font>

1354
01:19:43,581 --> 01:19:45,463
<font color=#FFFF5E>President's schedule always
changes last minute.</font>

1355
01:19:45,664 --> 01:19:48,024
<font color=#FFFF5E>This is the one day and date
he could be sure wouldn't move.</font>

1356
01:19:48,051 --> 01:19:50,160
<font color=#FFFF5E>Having my brother and I
leave the investigation</font>

1357
01:19:50,244 --> 01:19:51,513
<font color=#FFFF5E>was a setup from the start.</font>

1358
01:19:51,680 --> 01:19:52,680
<font color=#FFFF5E>Think about it.</font>

1359
01:19:52,882 --> 01:19:54,491
<font color=#FFFF5E>He hired us to fail.</font>

1360
01:19:56,163 --> 01:19:57,281
<font color=#FFFF5E>Get down!</font>

1361
01:20:44,389 --> 01:20:46,069
<font color=#FFFF5E>All right, it says we're
back in the clear.</font>

1362
01:20:46,160 --> 01:20:47,412
<font color=#FFFF5E>We've got four minutes to 91.</font>

1363
01:20:51,425 --> 01:20:53,305
<font color=#FFFF5E>Just gotta take care
of a little problem, first.</font>

1364
01:21:07,748 --> 01:21:08,748
<font color=#FFFF5E>Hold on!</font>

1365
01:21:11,222 --> 01:21:12,381
<font color=#FFFF5E>Woo!</font>

1366
01:21:16,239 --> 01:21:17,306
<font color=#FFFF5E>Marry her.</font>

1367
01:21:54,981 --> 01:21:56,195
<font color=#FFFF5E>No. We're fine here.</font>

1368
01:21:56,236 --> 01:21:58,276
<font color=#FFFF5E><i>A lightning storm in
Orlando has caused</i></font>

1369
01:21:58,320 --> 01:22:00,914
<font color=#FFFF5E><i>a horrific explosion at the DNC.</i></font>

1370
01:22:00,955 --> 01:22:03,731
<font color=#FFFF5E><i>There's no official word on the
whereabouts of the President...</i></font>

1371
01:22:04,033 --> 01:22:05,987
<font color=#FFFF5E>I don't know...
I don't know.</font>

1372
01:22:07,075 --> 01:22:09,204
<font color=#FFFF5E>I just can't get in touch with Jake.</font>

1373
01:22:09,406 --> 01:22:12,623
<font color=#FFFF5E><i>We have reports now on
explosions on the space station.</i></font>

1374
01:22:12,823 --> 01:22:14,078
<font color=#FFFF5E>Honey, the Orlando storm</font>

1375
01:22:14,132 --> 01:22:15,928
<font color=#FFFF5E>is getting really close
to your dad's place.</font>

1376
01:22:16,229 --> 01:22:19,919
<font color=#FFFF5E>I-I can't get through to him.
Has he texted you? Or...</font>

1377
01:22:20,119 --> 01:22:21,270
<font color=#FFFF5E>He's not there.</font>

1378
01:22:23,050 --> 01:22:24,088
<font color=#FFFF5E>He's there.</font>

1379
01:22:25,944 --> 01:22:28,367
<font color=#FFFF5E><i>On a major issue
on the space station.</i></font>

1380
01:22:33,145 --> 01:22:35,110
<font color=#FFFF5E><i>Attention all crews.</i></font>

1381
01:22:35,214 --> 01:22:37,047
<font color=#FFFF5E><i>Now loading final shuttle.</i></font>

1382
01:22:43,409 --> 01:22:47,290
<font color=#FFFF5E><i>Please board the designated
evacuation shuttle immediately.</i></font>

1383
01:22:47,491 --> 01:22:50,262
<font color=#FFFF5E><i>Shuttle launch sequence initiating.</i></font>

1384
01:22:50,901 --> 01:22:51,901
<font color=#FFFF5E>Jake.</font>

1385
01:22:52,572 --> 01:22:54,439
<font color=#FFFF5E>- I'm not comin'.
- What?</font>

1386
01:22:54,852 --> 01:22:56,432
<font color=#FFFF5E>When my brother
gets those kill codes,</font>

1387
01:22:56,490 --> 01:22:58,290
<font color=#FFFF5E>someone has to be here
to execute the program.</font>

1388
01:22:58,312 --> 01:22:59,551
<font color=#FFFF5E>No. We need to go.</font>

1389
01:22:59,752 --> 01:23:01,183
<font color=#FFFF5E>We haven't heard
from him in hours.</font>

1390
01:23:01,484 --> 01:23:02,784
<font color=#FFFF5E>I trust him.</font>

1391
01:23:02,952 --> 01:23:05,466
<font color=#FFFF5E>You know the reboot
has to be done manually.</font>

1392
01:23:05,668 --> 01:23:07,108
<font color=#FFFF5E>Then I stay.
I'm the commander.</font>

1393
01:23:07,158 --> 01:23:08,359
<font color=#FFFF5E>No.</font>

1394
01:23:08,959 --> 01:23:11,703
<font color=#FFFF5E>I'm the only one my brother
would trust with the codes, so.</font>

1395
01:23:12,777 --> 01:23:14,056
<font color=#FFFF5E>I need your holoframe.</font>

1396
01:23:18,989 --> 01:23:21,479
<font color=#FFFF5E>You have to insert it manually
at the core of the mainframe.</font>

1397
01:23:23,346 --> 01:23:24,573
<font color=#FFFF5E>You can find it, yes?</font>

1398
01:23:25,264 --> 01:23:26,311
<font color=#FFFF5E>- Yes.
- Good.</font>

1399
01:23:30,215 --> 01:23:31,368
<font color=#FFFF5E>Goodbye, Ute.</font>

1400
01:23:33,169 --> 01:23:35,176
<font color=#FFFF5E>Auf Wiedersehen, Jake.</font>

1401
01:23:44,499 --> 01:23:45,857
<font color=#FFFF5E>Pull over here.</font>

1402
01:23:46,402 --> 01:23:48,864
<font color=#FFFF5E>The President's beacon shows
him heading right towards us.</font>

1403
01:23:53,017 --> 01:23:54,785
<font color=#FFFF5E>You really wanna
drive back into that?</font>

1404
01:23:54,938 --> 01:23:59,105
<font color=#FFFF5E>Yeah, right after it passes,
I'll be the sole survivor...</font>

1405
01:23:59,306 --> 01:24:02,896
<font color=#FFFF5E>ready to be sworn in as the
next President of the United States.</font>

1406
01:24:14,244 --> 01:24:15,681
<font color=#FFFF5E>Here they come.</font>

1407
01:24:22,491 --> 01:24:23,491
<font color=#FFFF5E>Fire.</font>

1408
01:24:50,620 --> 01:24:53,140
<font color=#FFFF5E>You thought the President was
the only one who could be tracked?</font>

1409
01:25:02,078 --> 01:25:03,833
<font color=#FFFF5E>- How the hell did you?
- How?</font>

1410
01:25:04,344 --> 01:25:05,884
<font color=#FFFF5E>'Cause I'm the goddamn President</font>

1411
01:25:05,909 --> 01:25:07,571
<font color=#FFFF5E>of the United States of America.</font>

1412
01:25:07,967 --> 01:25:09,612
<font color=#FFFF5E>You're done, Leonard.</font>

1413
01:25:15,534 --> 01:25:16,724
<font color=#FFFF5E>He's all yours.</font>

1414
01:25:21,985 --> 01:25:23,105
<font color=#FFFF5E>Wait, wait, wait a minute.</font>

1415
01:25:23,296 --> 01:25:25,337
<font color=#FFFF5E>I've given you an opportunity,
Mr. President.</font>

1416
01:25:25,538 --> 01:25:27,081
<font color=#FFFF5E>You should take it.</font>

1417
01:25:27,182 --> 01:25:28,661
<font color=#FFFF5E>An opportunity?
Let him go.</font>

1418
01:25:29,773 --> 01:25:31,036
<font color=#FFFF5E>It's genocide, Leonard!</font>

1419
01:25:31,238 --> 01:25:34,002
<font color=#FFFF5E>You say genocide,
I say preemptive strike.</font>

1420
01:25:34,202 --> 01:25:35,202
<font color=#FFFF5E>You've lost your mind!</font>

1421
01:25:35,572 --> 01:25:38,585
<font color=#FFFF5E>Tomorrow, the sun will rise,
all our enemies will be gone.</font>

1422
01:25:38,986 --> 01:25:41,615
<font color=#FFFF5E>Wiped away as if
by the hand of God!</font>

1423
01:25:43,288 --> 01:25:44,593
<font color=#FFFF5E>Why would you do this?</font>

1424
01:25:44,794 --> 01:25:46,595
<font color=#FFFF5E>Because no one else would.</font>

1425
01:25:46,796 --> 01:25:49,009
<font color=#FFFF5E>I'm turning the clock
back to 1945...</font>

1426
01:25:49,210 --> 01:25:51,671
<font color=#FFFF5E>when America was
a shining city on a hill...</font>

1427
01:25:51,718 --> 01:25:53,570
<font color=#FFFF5E>not just a bank
disguised as a country.</font>

1428
01:25:53,696 --> 01:25:54,697
<font color=#FFFF5E>By playing God?</font>

1429
01:25:54,898 --> 01:25:57,642
<font color=#FFFF5E>What the hell is Dutch Boy
if not playing God?</font>

1430
01:25:57,843 --> 01:25:59,476
<font color=#FFFF5E>Ask Max, he knows.</font>

1431
01:25:59,777 --> 01:26:01,483
<font color=#FFFF5E>Science is all about playing God.</font>

1432
01:26:01,785 --> 01:26:04,244
<font color=#FFFF5E>Sometimes,
God doesn't play so nice.</font>

1433
01:26:04,945 --> 01:26:07,010
<font color=#FFFF5E>Yeah, well, you know what
my brother would say?</font>

1434
01:26:07,180 --> 01:26:08,180
<font color=#FFFF5E>What?</font>

1435
01:26:14,842 --> 01:26:16,353
<font color=#FFFF5E>Get him outta here.</font>

1436
01:26:18,450 --> 01:26:19,743
<font color=#FFFF5E>Let's go, Lawson!</font>

1437
01:26:21,839 --> 01:26:23,940
<font color=#FFFF5E>That's my fiancé.</font>

1438
01:27:19,739 --> 01:27:21,777
<font color=#FFFF5E>Get the President
to cover. Hurry!</font>

1439
01:27:29,288 --> 01:27:30,788
<font color=#FFFF5E>Mr. President.</font>

1440
01:27:31,144 --> 01:27:32,144
<font color=#FFFF5E>We got the kill codes.</font>

1441
01:27:32,314 --> 01:27:34,314
<font color=#FFFF5E>You'll have to hurry.
Station-controlled shut down.</font>

1442
01:27:34,414 --> 01:27:35,615
<font color=#FFFF5E>What about the crew?</font>

1443
01:27:35,816 --> 01:27:36,816
<font color=#FFFF5E>Safe.</font>

1444
01:27:36,918 --> 01:27:38,824
<font color=#FFFF5E>But Jake decided to stay.</font>

1445
01:27:38,925 --> 01:27:41,129
<font color=#FFFF5E>To reboot the satellites.</font>

1446
01:27:42,206 --> 01:27:43,606
<font color=#FFFF5E>Your brother's waitin' for you.</font>

1447
01:27:45,072 --> 01:27:46,829
<font color=#FFFF5E>Come on.</font>

1448
01:27:49,415 --> 01:27:51,089
<font color=#FFFF5E><i>Virtual conference initiating.</i></font>

1449
01:27:51,290 --> 01:27:52,290
<font color=#FFFF5E>Hey.</font>

1450
01:27:54,633 --> 01:27:55,633
<font color=#FFFF5E><i>Jake.</i></font>

1451
01:27:56,102 --> 01:27:57,595
<font color=#FFFF5E><i>Jake, it was Dekkom.</i></font>

1452
01:27:58,297 --> 01:28:00,493
<font color=#FFFF5E>Well, I did say
I might be right.</font>

1453
01:28:01,261 --> 01:28:02,261
<font color=#FFFF5E><i>Mr. President.</i></font>

1454
01:28:04,151 --> 01:28:05,151
<font color=#FFFF5E>How's Hannah?</font>

1455
01:28:05,418 --> 01:28:06,503
<font color=#FFFF5E>Oh, she's good, she's safe.</font>

1456
01:28:06,705 --> 01:28:07,977
<font color=#FFFF5E><i>Atlanta wasn't hit.</i></font>

1457
01:28:08,477 --> 01:28:09,696
<font color=#FFFF5E><i>Thank God.</i></font>

1458
01:28:10,971 --> 01:28:12,190
<font color=#FFFF5E><i>Identity verified.</i></font>

1459
01:28:12,250 --> 01:28:13,998
<font color=#FFFF5E><i>Shut down protocol
transfer initiating.</i></font>

1460
01:28:14,199 --> 01:28:15,986
<font color=#FFFF5E>It's gonna take
60 seconds to upload.</font>

1461
01:28:16,588 --> 01:28:18,068
<font color=#FFFF5E>Well, how long
till the self-destruct?</font>

1462
01:28:18,185 --> 01:28:19,240
<font color=#FFFF5E>Eight minutes.</font>

1463
01:28:19,641 --> 01:28:20,641
<font color=#FFFF5E>Give or take.</font>

1464
01:28:20,716 --> 01:28:21,817
<font color=#FFFF5E><i>Mr. Lawson...</i></font>

1465
01:28:22,824 --> 01:28:25,179
<font color=#FFFF5E><i>we thank you for your sacrifice.</i></font>

1466
01:28:31,855 --> 01:28:33,661
<font color=#FFFF5E><i>Wait. What the hell's goin' on?</i></font>

1467
01:28:33,862 --> 01:28:35,510
<font color=#FFFF5E>You've done your part, Max.</font>

1468
01:28:35,712 --> 01:28:37,012
<font color=#FFFF5E>Jake, what is goin' on?</font>

1469
01:28:37,214 --> 01:28:38,595
<font color=#FFFF5E>Now it's time for me to do mine.</font>

1470
01:28:40,734 --> 01:28:42,072
<font color=#FFFF5E>No, no, no.</font>

1471
01:28:42,472 --> 01:28:45,025
<font color=#FFFF5E>The kill codes don't stop
the self-destruct, do they?</font>

1472
01:28:46,514 --> 01:28:47,528
<font color=#FFFF5E>Do they?!</font>

1473
01:28:49,056 --> 01:28:50,056
<font color=#FFFF5E>No...</font>

1474
01:28:50,063 --> 01:28:51,272
<font color=#FFFF5E>only the geostorm.</font>

1475
01:28:51,473 --> 01:28:54,010
<font color=#FFFF5E>The station's self-destruct
can't be reversed.</font>

1476
01:28:55,566 --> 01:28:58,064
<font color=#FFFF5E>Come on, come on,
there must be a way, huh?</font>

1477
01:28:58,766 --> 01:29:00,987
<font color=#FFFF5E>Come on, it's all my fault.
I'm the one who put you up there.</font>

1478
01:29:00,988 --> 01:29:02,489
<font color=#FFFF5E>Hey, it's okay.</font>

1479
01:29:03,891 --> 01:29:06,249
<font color=#FFFF5E>I wanted to go.
It was my choice.</font>

1480
01:29:08,380 --> 01:29:09,605
<font color=#FFFF5E>God knows...</font>

1481
01:29:10,106 --> 01:29:12,039
<font color=#FFFF5E>I haven't always
made the right ones.</font>

1482
01:29:14,540 --> 01:29:16,288
<font color=#FFFF5E>You know, you were right,
little brother.</font>

1483
01:29:19,157 --> 01:29:21,102
<font color=#FFFF5E>I <i>was</i> supposed to look after you.</font>

1484
01:29:24,390 --> 01:29:26,258
<font color=#FFFF5E>But you looked after me.</font>

1485
01:29:30,542 --> 01:29:31,845
<font color=#FFFF5E>Can you forgive me?</font>

1486
01:29:32,791 --> 01:29:34,269
<font color=#FFFF5E>Yeah, always.</font>

1487
01:29:36,603 --> 01:29:38,164
<font color=#FFFF5E>Look after my little girl.</font>

1488
01:29:39,858 --> 01:29:41,720
<font color=#FFFF5E>Stay in her life.</font>

1489
01:29:42,221 --> 01:29:43,222
<font color=#FFFF5E>I will.</font>

1490
01:29:46,384 --> 01:29:48,425
<font color=#FFFF5E>Should've done this
a long time ago, huh?</font>

1491
01:29:48,826 --> 01:29:49,827
<font color=#FFFF5E>Yeah.</font>

1492
01:29:51,607 --> 01:29:53,068
<font color=#FFFF5E>You're a good man, Jake.</font>

1493
01:29:54,509 --> 01:29:55,575
<font color=#FFFF5E>I'll see you, kiddo.</font>

1494
01:29:57,666 --> 01:29:58,936
<font color=#FFFF5E><i>Transfer complete.</i></font>

1495
01:30:05,643 --> 01:30:09,874
<font color=#FFFF5E><i>Time to geostorm:
Five minutes, 51 seconds.</i></font>

1496
01:30:32,464 --> 01:30:35,498
<font color=#FFFF5E><i>Warning: Core rotation
has terminated.</i></font>

1497
01:30:38,321 --> 01:30:40,549
<font color=#FFFF5E><i>We don't know
what's happening up there­.</i></font>

1498
01:30:40,750 --> 01:30:42,695
<font color=#FFFF5E><i>We just know
the station has suffered</i></font>

1499
01:30:42,740 --> 01:30:44,792
<font color=#FFFF5E><i>a devastating accident
of some kind.</i></font>

1500
01:30:45,394 --> 01:30:48,545
<font color=#FFFF5E><i>We're being told now
it is beyond repair or salvation.</i></font>

1501
01:30:49,538 --> 01:30:50,538
<font color=#FFFF5E>Honey.</font>

1502
01:30:50,599 --> 01:30:51,899
<font color=#FFFF5E>He's coming back.</font>

1503
01:30:53,212 --> 01:30:54,430
<font color=#FFFF5E>He promised me.</font>

1504
01:30:54,583 --> 01:30:57,546
<font color=#FFFF5E><i>We will keep you updated
with any new developments.</i></font>

1505
01:31:18,637 --> 01:31:21,649
<font color=#FFFF5E><i>Self-destruct
entering phase four.</i></font>

1506
01:31:36,719 --> 01:31:37,719
<font color=#FFFF5E><i>Code invalid.</i></font>

1507
01:31:41,645 --> 01:31:42,794
<font color=#FFFF5E><i>Code invalid.</i></font>

1508
01:31:44,178 --> 01:31:45,258
<font color=#FFFF5E><i>Need a hand?</i></font>

1509
01:31:50,353 --> 01:31:51,616
<font color=#FFFF5E><i>Wrong door.</i></font>

1510
01:31:56,182 --> 01:31:57,182
<font color=#FFFF5E><i>What are you doing here?</i></font>

1511
01:31:57,371 --> 01:31:59,637
<font color=#FFFF5E><i>I told you I live here.</i></font>

1512
01:32:12,330 --> 01:32:15,512
<font color=#FFFF5E><i>Time to geostorm:
One minute, 40 seconds.</i></font>

1513
01:32:29,277 --> 01:32:30,784
<font color=#FFFF5E><i>Uploading kill codes.</i></font>

1514
01:32:47,986 --> 01:32:50,616
<font color=#FFFF5E><i>Satellite shut down in process.</i></font>

1515
01:32:53,625 --> 01:32:56,656
<font color=#FFFF5E><i>When the last satellite
cycles down, let me know.</i></font>

1516
01:32:56,944 --> 01:32:59,728
<font color=#FFFF5E><i>I'll manually reboot
the entire system.</i></font>

1517
01:32:59,930 --> 01:33:01,959
<font color=#FFFF5E><i>- That should flush out the virus.
- Okay.</i></font>

1518
01:33:25,551 --> 01:33:26,804
<font color=#FFFF5E><i>Five to go.</i></font>

1519
01:33:32,500 --> 01:33:33,516
<font color=#FFFF5E><i>Three.</i></font>

1520
01:33:33,660 --> 01:33:35,022
<font color=#FFFF5E><i>- Come on, baby.
- Two.</i></font>

1521
01:33:36,969 --> 01:33:37,969
<font color=#FFFF5E><i>And one.</i></font>

1522
01:33:40,491 --> 01:33:41,983
<font color=#FFFF5E><i>Manual reboot activated.</i></font>

1523
01:34:04,250 --> 01:34:05,855
<font color=#FFFF5E><i>Status: Rebooting.</i></font>

1524
01:34:06,155 --> 01:34:09,011
<font color=#FFFF5E><i>The net is back up.
The virus is gone.</i></font>

1525
01:34:09,977 --> 01:34:12,625
<font color=#FFFF5E><i>Transferring control
of the net back to NASA.</i></font>

1526
01:34:26,643 --> 01:34:27,739
<font color=#FFFF5E><i>Jake!</i></font>

1527
01:34:36,804 --> 01:34:38,000
<font color=#FFFF5E><i>I've got you!</i></font>

1528
01:34:38,157 --> 01:34:41,982
<font color=#FFFF5E><i>Warning: Self-destruct
entering final stage.</i></font>

1529
01:34:50,557 --> 01:34:51,708
<font color=#FFFF5E><i>Best seat in the house.</i></font>

1530
01:35:02,245 --> 01:35:03,245
<font color=#FFFF5E><i>Ute...</i></font>

1531
01:35:05,750 --> 01:35:07,368
<font color=#FFFF5E><i>Are you a believer in
the Hail Mary?</i></font>

1532
01:35:09,244 --> 01:35:11,677
<font color=#FFFF5E><i>Follow me.
We gotta get to the satellite.</i></font>

1533
01:35:51,218 --> 01:35:52,218
<font color=#FFFF5E><i>I've got you.</i></font>

1534
01:35:57,481 --> 01:35:59,410
<font color=#FFFF5E><i>We gotta get away
as far as we can</i></font>

1535
01:35:59,474 --> 01:36:01,012
<font color=#FFFF5E><i>before the final detonation.</i></font>

1536
01:36:02,016 --> 01:36:03,530
<font color=#FFFF5E><i>Dock releasing.</i></font>

1537
01:36:42,801 --> 01:36:46,324
<font color=#FFFF5E><i>And it appears we have lost
the space station.</i></font>

1538
01:36:46,611 --> 01:36:49,785
<font color=#FFFF5E><i>A tragic ending for the
two heroes still on board.</i></font>

1539
01:37:04,836 --> 01:37:06,308
<font color=#FFFF5E>Hey, Max, take a look.</font>

1540
01:37:09,444 --> 01:37:10,861
<font color=#FFFF5E>Picking up exhaust flares.</font>

1541
01:37:12,169 --> 01:37:13,595
<font color=#FFFF5E>And they're pulsing.</font>

1542
01:37:13,999 --> 01:37:15,371
<font color=#FFFF5E>In a mayday pattern.</font>

1543
01:37:23,820 --> 01:37:25,954
<font color=#FFFF5E>See if we could turn
one of the shuttles around.</font>

1544
01:37:36,089 --> 01:37:38,138
<font color=#FFFF5E><i>Hopefully, someone sees us.</i></font>

1545
01:37:42,077 --> 01:37:43,514
<font color=#FFFF5E><i>Fingers crossed.</i></font>

1546
01:38:16,360 --> 01:38:18,602
<font color=#FFFF5E><i>Hernandez, you son of a bitch!</i></font>

1547
01:38:19,239 --> 01:38:20,343
<font color=#FFFF5E>Thank the Mexican.</font>

1548
01:38:38,884 --> 01:38:41,148
<font color=#FFFF5E>Yes! Come here. Yes!</font>

1549
01:39:13,502 --> 01:39:15,027
<font color=#FFFF5E><i>A miracle indeed.</i></font>

1550
01:39:15,528 --> 01:39:17,496
<font color=#FFFF5E><i>The shuttle you see
is bringing home</i></font>

1551
01:39:17,539 --> 01:39:20,829
<font color=#FFFF5E><i>all the ISS crew members
who remained on the station.</i></font>

1552
01:39:35,558 --> 01:39:39,140
<font color=#FFFF5E>Hi, Jake. I'm Sarah,
Max's fiancée.</font>

1553
01:39:39,741 --> 01:39:41,255
<font color=#FFFF5E>Well, welcome to the family.</font>

1554
01:39:41,455 --> 01:39:43,693
<font color=#FFFF5E>Well done, well done.
Both of you.</font>

1555
01:39:44,494 --> 01:39:46,348
<font color=#FFFF5E>Sorry I doubted you,
Mr. President.</font>

1556
01:39:46,549 --> 01:39:48,390
<font color=#FFFF5E>Yeah, well,
you were wrong, Jake.</font>

1557
01:39:48,434 --> 01:39:49,479
<font color=#FFFF5E>Again.</font>

1558
01:39:49,588 --> 01:39:51,612
<font color=#FFFF5E>Well, how many times
do I have to tell you?</font>

1559
01:39:51,914 --> 01:39:53,081
<font color=#FFFF5E>Never listen to me.</font>

1560
01:40:01,929 --> 01:40:03,440
<font color=#FFFF5E>God, it's good to have you back.</font>

1561
01:40:03,642 --> 01:40:04,914
<font color=#FFFF5E>Good to be back.</font>

1562
01:40:30,670 --> 01:40:32,734
<font color=#FFFF5E>It's a nice place
you got here, Jake.</font>

1563
01:40:33,598 --> 01:40:34,598
<font color=#FFFF5E>Thank you.</font>

1564
01:40:35,965 --> 01:40:37,591
<font color=#FFFF5E>So, when you heading back up?</font>

1565
01:40:38,677 --> 01:40:39,976
<font color=#FFFF5E>- In a week.
- Yeah?</font>

1566
01:40:40,477 --> 01:40:42,196
<font color=#FFFF5E>Yeah, a lot of work left.</font>

1567
01:40:43,503 --> 01:40:45,495
<font color=#FFFF5E>But I'll be back.</font>

1568
01:40:46,927 --> 01:40:47,927
<font color=#FFFF5E>I know.</font>

1569
01:40:57,958 --> 01:40:59,958
<font color=#FFFF5E>- This sucks.
- Yeah, seriously, this is so boring.</font>

1570
01:41:00,037 --> 01:41:02,089
<font color=#FFFF5E>You know what?
I can't do this for another second.</font>

1571
01:41:02,279 --> 01:41:04,039
<font color=#FFFF5E>Why'd you make us
do this in the first place?</font>

1572
01:41:04,043 --> 01:41:05,900
<font color=#FFFF5E>I don't know.
I was tryin' to relive a moment.</font>

1573
01:41:06,102 --> 01:41:07,757
<font color=#FFFF5E>Moment? W-What moment?</font>

1574
01:41:08,122 --> 01:41:09,432
<font color=#FFFF5E>We never went fishing with Dad.</font>

1575
01:41:09,489 --> 01:41:10,649
<font color=#FFFF5E>You made that whole story up.</font>

1576
01:41:10,878 --> 01:41:12,598
<font color=#FFFF5E>Yeah, but that was
a good story though, huh?</font>

1577
01:41:12,781 --> 01:41:14,158
<font color=#FFFF5E>You gotta admit that.</font>

1578
01:41:14,360 --> 01:41:16,205
<font color=#FFFF5E>It had a moral and everything.</font>

1579
01:41:16,407 --> 01:41:18,130
<font color=#FFFF5E>Moral? What moral?</font>

1580
01:41:21,990 --> 01:41:23,738
<font color=#FFFF5E><i>You can't undo the past.</i></font>

1581
01:41:23,938 --> 01:41:25,832
<font color=#FFFF5E><i>All you can do
is face what's ahead.</i></font>

1582
01:41:26,533 --> 01:41:28,500
<font color=#FFFF5E><i>NASA maintained the
satellites while</i></font>

1583
01:41:28,525 --> 01:41:30,141
<font color=#FFFF5E><i>we rebuilt the space station.</i></font>

1584
01:41:30,643 --> 01:41:33,080
<font color=#FFFF5E><i>We made it safer,
made it stronger.</i></font>

1585
01:41:33,130 --> 01:41:35,378
<font color=#FFFF5E><i>It belongs to all of us now.</i></font>

1586
01:41:35,809 --> 01:41:37,793
<font color=#FFFF5E><i>One planet, one people.</i></font>

1587
01:41:38,795 --> 01:41:41,762
<font color=#FFFF5E><i>And as long as we remember
that we share one future...</i></font>

1588
01:41:41,812 --> 01:41:43,778
<font color=#FFFF5E><i>we will survive.</i></font>

